data.description: Experience the allure of waterfront living with this exceptional residence nestled along the tranquil shores.  Step inside to a world of coastal elegance, where vaulted ceilings, abundant natural light, and a thoughtfully designed split-floor plan create an inviting and harmonious living experience. Featuring 4 spacious bedrooms & 3 bathrooms, this island dream home boasts a well-appointed kitchen with breakfast area & formal dining area along with a decorous wet bar perfect for all of your entertaining needs. The expansive master suite comes complete with an adjoining office or potential 5th bedroom space. You’ll be sure to love the sweeping water views in the master bathroom which has a jetted tub and cultured marble walk-in shower. Further enhancing its appeal, this exceptional home offers a private dock with an additional floating dock and is located on tidal creek. Embrace coastal living at its finest in this Tybee waterfront jewel that is STVR eligible with no city taxes!
